attachments.title: MDX-40A | CNC Mill | Benchtop CNC Mill | CNC Engraving Machine | Roland DGA
attachments.text: The MDX-40 desktop SRP system can mill a wide range of low cost, non-proprietary materials including ABS, delrin, nylon, and tooling board. It lets engineers create functional prototypes to testing.
